<div class="l-top">
  <div class="p-top-kv">
    <p class="p-top-lead">空気のコントロールを通じて<br class="sp-view">快適空間を守る</p>
    <div class="swiper-container swiper-init">
      <div class="swiper-wrapper">
        <div class="swiper-slide"><img src="<%- d.path %>assets/images/top/kv1.jpg" alt="" width="980" height="620"></div>
        <div class="swiper-slide"><img src="<%- d.path %>assets/images/top/kv2.jpg" alt="" width="980" height="620"></div>
        <div class="swiper-slide"><img src="<%- d.path %>assets/images/top/kv3.jpg" alt="" width="980" height="620"></div>
        <div class="swiper-slide"><img src="<%- d.path %>assets/images/top/kv4.jpg" alt="" width="980" height="620"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="p-top-wave">
    <canvas class="c-wave-canvas"></canvas>
  </div>
  <div class="p-top-content">
    <div class="p-top-cards">
        <section class="p-top-card p-top-card--wide">
            <h2 class="p-top-card__title">Introduction</h2>
						<p class="p-top-card__en">サンエス工業を語る</p>
            <div class="p-top-card__link">
                <a href="<%- d.path %>introduction/" class="c-button p-top-card__button">快適な空気を作る３つの要素</a>
                <a href="<%- d.path %>introduction/02/" class="c-button p-top-card__button">サンエスらしさって何だろう</a>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="p-top-card">
            <h2 class="p-top-card__title">Business Lineup</h2>
						<p class="p-top-card__en">事業案内</p>
            <div class="p-top-card__link">
                <a href="<%- d.path %>business/silencer/" class="c-button p-top-card__button">消音部門</a>
                <a href="<%- d.path %>business/air-conditioning/" class="c-button p-top-card__button">空調部門</a>
                <a href="<%- d.path %>business/duct/" class="c-button p-top-card__button">ダクト部門</a>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="p-top-card">
            <h2 class="p-top-card__title">About us</h2>
						<p class="p-top-card__en">会社案内</p>
            <div class="p-top-card__link">
                <a href="<%- d.path %>company/" class="c-button p-top-card__button is-large">企業情報</a>
